// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2231 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b83f64a5-510c-575e-acdf-92be30309eea

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
